Description:
On this map you will face a maze of high school, in your way, find your enemies and the only way to kill them is a knife!
If you reach the center of the map you will find a machine that will teleport you to a room where you have full view of the maze and the weapons you will find on the wall that you can kill their enemies and they never know where you are, but be careful they do not appear behind you and puff "Humiliation!"
